                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "This mod is given at the penultimate mission of The Sacrifice , automatically ranked to level 5. Additional unranked mods can be bought from Cephalon Simaris for 100,000 Standing 100,000 ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
