                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "This mod outperforms Steel Fiber from rank 8 when using 2 set pieces and from rank 6 when using 3."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Umbral Fiber",
                  "pageId": 1312614,
                  "revisionId": 2792488,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Umbra mods have a unique polarity, whose matching polarity can currently only be found on Excalibur Umbra , Exalted Umbra Blade , and the Skiajati . It is possible to (re-)add a polarity to a mod slot but only through the use of Umbra Forma , which can be obtained either directly, from Nightwave , or built with blueprints purchasable once every 8 weeks with Steel Essence . Given the extremely limited rate of acquisition, it is advised not to re-Forma any mod slot with an polarity."
                }
